# =============================================================================
# .gitignore for the thesis code repository
# Keeps: notebook, README, requirements/environment, raw Hillstrom data,
#        benchmark variants, and final result tables/figures.
# Excludes: the bulky differentially-private synthetic datasets (regenerated by
#        thesis_pipeline.ipynb), the external private-pgm clone, and local cruft.
# =============================================================================

# --- Regenerable synthetic datasets (~1.3 GB; recreated on a full notebook run) ---
data/main_synthetic_mst/
**/synthetic_mst/

# --- Local scratch notebooks ---
Untitled.ipynb
anaconda_projects/

# --- Jupyter / Python ---
.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/
.virtual_documents/
**/.virtual_documents/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
